messages.message:
think i found the problem… changed the udf a bit to let it return `type(text)` where text is the function input, and  `test_json_loads_from_input('[]')` returns `<type 'list'>` in Refiner… so this is probably a bug with our Refiner parser. Somehow `'[]'` got parsed as a list instead of a string.

I created an Asana task: https://app.asana.com/0/977607438764353/1122958847205298/f
@Jonathan Shih is this something that you are familiar with since you’ve been looking at the parser list code?
@Kerry @dlluncor ah yeah this seems like a bug with my bugfix for parsing [] as a list. I think I need to make a change to the regex. Will look into it
